-dyn_zip_p 0.0,0.0,1.0 # Proportion of constant power, constant current, and constant impedance respectively for the real power loads
-dyn_zip_q 0.0,0.0,1.0 # Proportion of constant power, constant current, and constant impedance respectively for the reactive power loads


